				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ahhh, the endless debate of who is the best.  Myself I play a mage. I think its a great character to play.  I agree that mages cannot handle more than one mob at a time when soloing. Im not sure about a necro cause ive never really seen one solo more than one mob. But if anyone was able to im sure the necro would be it. I do think mages are better for grouping, but again I play a mage, I have never played a necro before. Im not to clear on Dots doing more than Dds over time, I just know that mages get the second best Dds in the game. As for the person way back in the list saying the root sucks and that we should be able to cast root ourselves and nuke, that is crap. Earth pets are great for there root and attack. They make us able to lay the smackith down on there candyasses as fast as we want without the mob coming at us.  About dueling eachother to see who is best. In my opinion (being that they are 55+) I think the wizzy would own all (never played one). There dds get so powerfull one hit would kill any player in the game.  Root pet, blast pet, pet dead. &quot;Uh oh&quot; says mage/necro, &quot;what do i do n@##$&quot; to late wizzy got off second dd, bye bye mage/necro hehe. Well it might not go that well but I think that a wizzy that knows what there doing could manage quite well.  Anyways I play a mage only, I love my mage, I have no gripes about it. Sorry to whoever bitches about how we suck we cant have everything, if we did everyone would be a mage/god.<BR>
