				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok, yes necro's are the best soloers in the game. Not a druid or a magician but yes a necro. A Magicians role is completly different than one of a wizard  or a necro. A magicians job is to supply a group w/what ever we can summon up and make life a bit easier. Another role (a more major role) is to do lots and lots of damage in a short amount of time. Of course we are secondary in the dmg department than wizards are, because if we werent. Then the game would be a little off balance. Every person  has thier role, even though we (Magicians) rather solo than group, if thiers no wizard around a magician is a very good back up.<BR>
<BR>
Mckerrn Leviathan<BR>
